      "voiceName": "Trevor Noah",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "Hey Chandler, I\u2019m adding a third show. \nYes, you heard that right. A new date has just been added. Don\u2019t miss your chance to see me live.\n\nPresale: March 17 @ 10AM MST\nCode: SUMMER\n\nGeneral On Sale: March 20 @ 10AM MST\n\nSee you there!",
