    {
      "voiceId": "trevor-noah",
      "voiceName": "Trevor Noah",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "Let me tell you something: Fame won\u2019t make you happy. \n\nMost people think fame will make them happy.\n\nBut according to Arthur C. Brooks, fame often creates the opposite effect.\n\nWatch the full episode on my YouTube channel to understand the real science of happiness.\n\nVideo",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/Trevornoah/status/2033301210787414237",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-15T21:56:00+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "trevor-noah",
      "voiceName": "Trevor Noah",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "Is the life plan everyone was told wrong? \n\nGet good grades.\nGet a good job.\nBuy a house.\nThen you\u2019ll be happy. Really?\n\nVideo",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/Trevornoah/status/2032952915678179446",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-14T22:52:00+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "trevor-noah",
      "voiceName": "Trevor Noah",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "That is how I became a soccer fan... Anyone else?\n\nVideo",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/Trevornoah/status/2032574421706354838",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-13T21:48:00+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "trevor-noah",
      "voiceName": "Trevor Noah",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "Did Disney lie to us?\n\nWe grew up believing the good guy always wins. Turns out\u2026 the real world doesn\u2019t work like that.\n\nVideo",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/Trevornoah/status/2032192406536270127",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-12T20:30:00+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
